               <floruit notBefore="1508" notAfter="1531">He was a warlord of 
              
                  <persName ref="PRS6229LebnaDe">    
                     <roleName type="title">ʾaṣe</roleName> 
                     Lǝbna Dǝngǝl</persName>.
                  He was also a governor of the most important frontier province 
                  of the Christian kingdom, <placeName ref="LOC3061Fataga">Faṭagār</placeName>
                  where he was successful to repel the Muslim raiders at first. But he was 
                  sent by 
                  <persName ref="PRS6229LebnaDe">
                     <roleName type="title">ʾaṣe</roleName> 
                     Lǝbna Dǝngǝl</persName> to withstand the Muslim forces in another area where he was killed by 
                  <persName ref="PRS1324AbuBakr">Abū Bakr b. Yimāǧ Ahmad</persName>.
